HEADWORD: Unrivaled
<hw>Un*ri"valed</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Having no rival;
without a competitor; peerless.</def> <altsp>[Spelt also
<asp>unrivalled</asp>.]</altsp> <rj><au>Pope.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
